{"tid":1485588,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"同大家解釋下乜野叫「無大台、大台、捉鬼」","createTime":"2019-08-18T16:15:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:07.000Z","uid":103569,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"c5893956870581d612c8b5151d890ce306010588","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:15:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜野係無大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n無大台＝去中央化、自發、多元：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">去中央化</span><br />\n令到政治上可以be water，<br />\n「領袖」唔會受到過大壓力，<br />\n「群眾」都唔洗再驚被背叛，<br />\n對家更加搵唔到對頭人做離間。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">自發</span><br />\n每個人唔會因為需要接收指令先做野，<br />\n行動變得有效率，唔似啲冒警咁係條街企最少半個鐘再跑500米。<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">多元</span><br />\n每個人擅長野唔一樣，自己會搵到自覺最適合嘅角色；<br />\n更重要係，我地知道自己唔係樣樣叻，<br />\n所以一定會有人做啲同自己唔同嘅野，<br />\n百花齊放，互補不足，產生協同效應。<br />\n<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />乜野叫大台<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n好多人會覺得「大台」等於由上而下司令台， 又或者係政客吸光舞台，但係其實：<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">大台就係「強逼」、「統一」、「共識」三為一體。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n例子一：「今日只係和理非」<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\">強逼</span> 所有人只可以和理非<br />\n2. <span style=\"color: red;\">統一</span> 所有人只可以和理非<br />\n3. 覺得今日和理非係全世界 <span style=\"color: red;\">共識</span><br />\n所以，<span style=\"color: red;\">「今日只係和理非」哩句就係大台。</span><br />\n醒目嘅你睇到哩到，你就知大台關鍵唔係共識，都唔係統一，而係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">強逼</span></span>。<br />\n<br />\n例子二：「光復香港，時代革命」<br />\n1. 無人強逼你認同／叫出口<br />\n2. 無人話過要綱領統一<br />\n（就算五大訴求都好，提出額外野都無人反對你）<br />\n3. 大家都好忙，你唔需要同人就哩句口號產生共識<br />\n所以，「光復香港，時代革命」就唔係大台。<br />\n（如果覺得口號太兒戲，可以用五大訴求run多次，都唔係大台）<br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<br />\n所以，今晚小部分「激進和非理」指出「邊個留低邊個係鬼呀」，就係：<br />\n1+2. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">強逼＋統一</span></span> 所有人離開現場；唔離開甚至就唔係自己人<br />\n3. 自覺行完就走係全世界<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">共識</span></span><br />\n<br />\n簡單啲，咁樣嘅自我離間，就係<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: large;\">大台思維走火入魔之極致</span></span>。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－－<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />點樣捉鬼好<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n其實全部無樣睇架，靠外貌同裝備去睇真係太低智啦，又花心神。<br />\n<br />\n總之：<br />\n1. <span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">唔好做街頭版中計黨</span></span><br />\n唔好認定陣地戰、過激行為就係鬼；用下個腦，考慮當刻風險成效，現場自決。<br />\n<br />\n2. 鬼永遠同01一樣：<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: small;\">「關鍵時刻，體態盡現」</span></span><br />\n電光石火，有人阻你，想捉你落地，仲要冒埋警，你唔搞死、搞盲佢你已經好厚道。<br />\n<br />\n等我學政府先<br />\n<br />\n完<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83033bf75057c9fa025339b342bc998ef73e6c7f","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:16:52.000Z","msg":"自推*10"},{"pid":"1b1e7d374cc14a04a77435dab63a36827a1e8dfd","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:17:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f1d8f42154b06544f697a6a072d66ba3f8eb52d","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:17:26.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9b1a522a0e94adba687d1cfc8e9dc2921f4b1594","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:17:41.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"72e8bd83be96598859aa923728a88257efcdbc9b","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:17:51.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02ab112783282870c5296533ee27524e8d9ea380","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:18:42.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"eb06a867d495227e4187ca4ed582bd2ecf6a7b58","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:21:31.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"9435d3ab7b2642da734296c49d616bc583699535","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:22:15.000Z","msg":"較錯字體大細<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />大家要用放大鏡"},{"pid":"5e7446d22d15f5ef2fd00f4560b0db1f844e31e9","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:23:13.000Z","msg":"利申番先：<br />\n<br />\n和理非唔係問題，大台先係問題；<br />\n唔係自己係大台嘅大台，就係問題中嘅問題！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b16aa33ebc77b54d34bf88163d3fb81ef4c7b1f2","tid":1485588,"uid":103569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-18T16:26:07.000Z","msg":"推"}]}